OL,3,CMarketing of iPlayer at the expense
OL,4,Cof BBC One
OL,6,GIs it time for the BBC to reassert
OL,7,Gthe primacy of BBC One?
OL,9,FIt should not need to be said. It is
OL,10,Fthe corporation's flagship service
OL,11,Ffor all of us and for many of those
OL,12,Fwho are light BBC viewers it IS the
OL,13,FBBC.
OL,15,FBut BBC marketing can increasingly
OL,16,Fgive the impression that the iPlayer
OL,17,Fmatters more.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/9
