OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F149A1701784249
OL,3,CMarketing of iPlayer at the expense
OL,4,Cof BBC One
OL,6,FIt's safe to say that the final total
OL,7,Fwill be significantly higher once
OL,8,FiPlayer hits are included. But it's
OL,9,Falso safe to say that many of those
OL,10,Fwho watch on iPlayer will either have
OL,11,Fbeen out last night or only decided
OL,12,Fto watch later after hearing good
OL,13,Freviews.
OL,15,FIn other words, for a channel like
OL,16,FBBC One there should be no sense of a
OL,17,Ffundamental historic shift ` just an
OL,18,Fevolution. Live viewing and catch up
OL,19,Fcan work positively together to
OL,20,Fensure good programmes reach as many
OL,21,Fpeople as possible.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
