OL,3,CMarketing of iPlayer at the expense
OL,4,Cof BBC One
OL,6,FThe new series of the thriller Vigil
OL,7,Fbegins soon. The six episodes will be
OL,8,Fshown across two weeks on Sundays,
OL,9,FMondays and Tuesdays.
OL,11,FThe series will drop on iPlayer in
OL,12,Ftwo batches ` the first three
OL,13,Fepisodes will appear on iPlayer on
OL,14,Fthe first Sunday with the second
OL,15,Fthree becoming available seven days
OL,16,Flater.
OL,18,FThe simple truth is that BBC One
OL,19,Fshould be the home of big premieres `
OL,20,Fthey bring people together and, even
OL,21,Ftoday, the glow of one big/special
OL,22,Fprogramme can reflect on others.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/9
