OL,3,CMarketing of iPlayer at the expense
OL,4,Cof BBC One
OL,6,FThere may be a case for a slight
OL,7,Ftweak to BBC One's remit though.
OL,8,FShould there be an even greater
OL,9,Femphasis on live broadcasting and
OL,10,Fflagship brands?
OL,12,FIt was interesting that BBC Sport
OL,13,Fconfirmed this week that some Women's
OL,14,FWorld Cup games had been shown on One
OL,15,Fin the full knowledge that the
OL,16,Fchannel's headline ratings might
OL,17,Fsuffer.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
