OL,3,CMarketing of iPlayer at the expense
OL,4,Cof BBC One
OL,6,FFor instance, the main Mastermind
OL,7,Fseries and University Challenge could
OL,8,Feasily move across. It was a
OL,9,Fsurprising but welcome move to see
OL,10,Fthe gentle Scottish comedy Two Doors
OL,11,FDown jump to the main channel last
OL,12,Fweek.
OL,14,FWith slots freed up, BBC Two could
OL,15,Fthen regain an even clearer sense of
OL,16,Fits old role as a home to innovation
OL,17,Fand special tastes and interests `
OL,18,Fsurely no bad thing if BBC Four does
OL,19,Fgo online only at some point?
OL,21,FBut in the short term, here's a very
OL,22,Fclear message to BBC marketing.
